title: Score 1,111 points in a round of Big Chinchompa
description: The Big chinchompa D&D starts every hour, at xx:30. Nyriki Tapio, found in a house in the Tree Gnome Stronghold, can help you get there. You are allowed to train Hunter between games.

description: Requires completion of the Broken Home quest atleast once before the challenges can be attempted. The challenges are: Complete a replay without dying, complete a replay using only one healing item or less, and complete a replay in less than 37 minutes.

title: Complete all the unabridged Fremennik Sagas
description: A Dungeoneering level of 71 and a Strength level of 75 are required. The memory fragments can be rarely found in Dungeoneering floors, keep an eye out.

title: Super Duper Secret Task #9
description: Complete 25 Chimp ice deliveries. Requires completion of the Do No Evil quest. Fastest route is the Balloon method listed on the wiki. Fastest route to buy Ice from the Monkey Colony is Glory to Al Kharid, Carpet to Colony. Blame Jack.

title: Recover all of Bandos' memories
description: They can be found all over Yu'biusk after completion of the Mighty Fall quest.

title: Find all Troublesome Crystals in Prifddinas
description: Some can be picked up, some require you to do something first. An Agility level of 77 and a Farming level of 75 are required as well as completion of the Plague's End quest.

title: Unlock all Eagle transport routes and build the 3 Rope racks found next to them
description: Requires completion of the Eagles' Peak quest and the Back to my Roots quest. A Teasing stick is required to unlock the Feldip route.

title: Create 150 Saradomin brews (3)
description: Saradomin brews can be created by mixing a clean Toadflax with a crushed bird's nest in a vial of water. This requires a Herblore level of 81. Bird's nests are easily obtained by Miscellenia workers gathering logs.

title: Create 150 Super antifire potions (3)
description: Super antifire potions can be created by mixing a phoenix feather with an antifire potion. This requires a Herblore level of 85.

title: Create a Super invention potion, and take a sip, they taste surprisingly good!
description: Super invention potions can be created by mixing a spider fang, with an invention potion. This requires a Herblore level of 87.

title: Create 150 Extreme defence potions (3)
description: Extreme defence potions can be created by mixing a Super defence potion (3) with a Lantadyme. This requires a Herblore level of 90.

title: Create one of each pouch made from Gold Charms
description: A list of the pouches and their requirements can be found on the wiki. A Summoning level of 71 is required.

title: Create 10 Obsidian golem pouches
description: Obsidian golems are made by using a Summoning pouch on a Summoning obelisk with 195 spirit shards, a blue charm and an obsidian charm. This requires a Summoning level of 73.

title: Create 10 Adamant minotaur pouches
description: Adamant minotaurs are made by using a Summoning pouch on a Summoning obelisk with 144 spirit shards, a blue charm, an adamant bar and a Summoning level of 76.

title: Create 10 Moss titan pouches
description: Moss titans are made by using a Summoning pouch on a Summoning obelisk with 202 spirit shards, a blue charm, an earth talisman and a Summoning level of 79.

title: Successfully cook 800 Green blubber jellyfish
description: Green blubbers can be caught in the Deep Sea Fishing Hub, requiring a Fishing level of 68 to catch and a Cooking level of 72 to cook.

title: Help Arod the environmentalist
description: Catch one of each of the creatures found on Mazcab. A Hunter level of 70 is required.

title: Super Duper Secret task #14
description: Obtain an Ancient scroll. To do this, you must first obtain a Rusty Chest. Good luck.

title: Obtain the Distorted engrammeter
description: A fully upgraded Engrammeter changes into the distorted version. This requires the completion of the Mahjarrat Memories miniquest, and the Fate of the Gods quest.

title: Obtain a Dark bow
description: A Slayer level of 90 is required to harm Dark beasts. It has a drop-rate of 1/1024.

title: Obtain a Staff of Light
description: The staff can be obtained from Ice strykewyrms, requiring a Slayer level of 93 to harm, as well as wearing a Fire or TokHaar cape. It has a drop rate of 1/512.

title: Obtain a Whip vine
description: The Whip vine is dropped by Jadinko guards and males requiring a Slayer level of 86 and 91 to harm, respectively. They can be found in the Jadinko Lair north of the Herblore Habitat.

title: Obtain a unique from Tormented demons
description: Unlocked upon completion of the While Guthix Sleeps quest. The demons require two combat styles to kill and a Silver- or Darklight to remove their shield. The stat-boosting effect from the Stone of Jas obtained in the Glacor cave works for Tormented demons.

title: Obtain the Brackish blade
description: Dropped by 'Rum'-pumped crabs which can be accessed with partial completion of the Clockwork Syringe quest.

title: Obtain a unique from Glacors
description: Glacors can be accessed after completion of the Ritual of the Mahjarrat quest. They can be reached using the Fairy Ring Code A K Q.

title: Unlock the ""of the Iowerth"" title
description: Complete 8 Dark Beast tasks assigned by Movran.

title: Obtain a breedable pair of Jadinkos and put them in the medium pen on the Ranch out of Time
description: A Farming level of 76 and a Construction level of 80 are required. They can be obtained by hunting various species of Jadinkos, and can be kept in the medium paddock on the Ranch out of Time

title: Obtain a breedable pair of Zygomites
description: A Farming level of 81 is required to breed them. They can be obtained by harvesting various mushrooms, at a 1/50 rate while harvesting a mushroom patch, and at a 1/400 rate when foraging clusters in the Arc.

title: Obtain a breedable pair of dragons
description: A Farming level of 92 is required. They can be obtained by killing green, blue, red or black dragons at a rate of 1/2000.

title: Obtain a unique from TzHaar
description: One unique from Mej, 3 uniques from Xil, the cape is dropped by all and the Ket-Om and the shield are dropped by the Xil and Ket.

title: Unlock the 7th tier of reputation with the Imperial district of Menaphos
description: Reputation can be obtained through various skilling activities in Menaphos; furthermore, squashing Corrupted scarabs and using the Soul Obelisk awards large quantities of reputation, too.

title: Obtain and show a uniquely coloured party hat to the Wise Old Man
description: The chromatic partyhat is obtained from opening a mystery gift, purchased from Thessalia in New Varrock for 200,000 Zemomarks. Wise Old Man can be found in Draynor Village.

title: Cower behind the Chosen Commander
description: Speak to General Wartface or General Bentnoze after the completion of the Chosen Commander and claim a Goblin Cower Shield

title: Locate and read the “Malleus Daemoniorum”
description: The book can be claimed by speaking to Brother Celerity. Mains must have taken part in a Demon Flash Mob prior to speaking to Celerity.

title: Locate and read “The Explorer’s notes”
description: The book can be found in the Keldagrim Libraries.

title: Locate and read “Grondaban’s Stalker notes”
description: The book can be found near the portal in the northern section of the Stalker Dungeon. Access to the dungeon requires completion of the Dishonour Among Thieves quest.

title: Discover all memories in each chapter of the Needle Skips quest
description: A medium experience lamp can be claimed from Megan west of Piscatoris upon completion.

title: Super Duper Secret Task #17
description: Create the Necklace of Charos from the 5 necklace trinkets scattered throughout Gielinor. Combine trinkets with the Old Necklace obtained upon completion of the You Are It quest.The Branches of Darkmeyer quest is required to obtain one of the trinkets.

title: Obtain the Crondis Mask and Nekhakha
description: Crondis’ Tomb can be accessed upon completion of the Crocodile Tears quest. A Constitution level of 80 is required. The tomb can be accessed within Crondis’ Pyramid in the Ports District of Menaphos.

title: Obtain the Het Mask and Heka
description: Hets tomb can be accessed upon the completion of the Our Man in the North quest. A Strength level of 80 is required.

title: Persuade Ramarno to share his knowledge of Smithing
description: Hand Ramarno a Redberry pie upon completion of the Defender of Varrock quest. Ramarno can be found by the Sacred Forge. A light source is required.

title: Teach Darren Lightfinger a trick or two
description: Speak to Darren Lightfinger and agree to teach him some tips. After speaking to Darren, pickpocket the training dummy, which requires a Thieving level of 62. After each pickpocket there will be additional dialogue until completion.

title: Unveil the mysteries of the TokHaar
description: Fully interact with and claim the experience from the mysterious and submerged statues upon completion of the One of a Kind quest.

title: Show the Bartender of the Rusty Anchor captain Braindeath’s mark
description: Upon showing the Bartender the mark, you’ll be reimbursed for all beers bought during the Rocking Out quest.

title: Locate and read “Scabarite Notes”
description: Collect all 19 Scabarite Notes by killing Skeletons, Dried Zombies, and Scabarites and adding them to the Scabaras research after the completion of the Dealing with Scabaras quest and the Scabarites Notes miniquest. The last 2 pages can be found in two chests below the plateau. Refer to the wiki for further details.

title: Claim the Divination lamp from Mr Mordaut
description: Mr. Mordaut can be found behind the stairs in Varrock Museum and will hand you a Divination experience lamp upon completion of the One of a Kind quest.

title: Fully Complete the Song from the Depths quest
description: Obtain the additional Constitution experience upon completion of the Song from the Depths quest, requiring a Constitution level of 80. Refer to the wiki for further details.

title: Visit all portals to the Spirit realm
description: There are 8 Portals to enter upon completion of the Summer’s End quest. Entering the portals require Jennica’s Ring to be worn. Refer to the wiki for the portals’ locations.

title: Locate and read the “Magister’s Journal”
description: Obtain all of the Magister’s Journal from either The Magister, or monsters in the Sophanem Slayer Dungeon. A Slayer level of 88 and completion of the Jack of Spades quest is required.

title: Claim Bill's reward
description: Speak to Bill Teach upon completion of the Cabin Fever quest to claim 10,000 coins from him. Bill can be found on the Port Phasmatys docks or on Mos Le’ Harmless.

title: Fully complete the Tai Bwo Wannai Trio quest
description: The Brothers can be found in each of the three huts on the southern wall of the village.

title: Obtain a Tooth creature
description: Claim the Tooth Creature from the Tooth Fairy by giving her a variety of teeth. Refer to the wiki for further details.

title: Reunite Irwinsson with his lost compass
description: A broken compass can be found in a damaged backpack at the shipwreck on the western coast of Anachronia, while a compass arrow can be obtained upon skinning any Big Game Hunter creature. The arrow can be attached to the broken compass and repaired by Irwinsonn who can be found by the Anachronia Lodestone.

title: Lay Arrav to rest
description: Put Arrav to rest upon completion of the Ritual of the Mahjarrat quest. Arrav can be found north east of the Ritual Marker along the wall of the Ice Fortress. Ghorrock can be accessed using the boat at the Rellekka hunter area.

title: Have an epilogue experience after While Guthix Sleeps
description: Upon completion of the While Guthix Sleeps quest, speak to Idria or Silif in the White Knights Castle.

title: Round up a Love Story
description: Two post-quest rewards are available upon completion of the Love Story quest by returning Mabel’s ring to Mabel who can be found east of the Draynor Lodestone, and by chopping down the Guard in Tree west of the Draynor Bank.

title: Claim and presume ownership of several rewards from the Statue of Death
description: Four post-quest rewards are available upon completion of the Missing, Presumed Death quest. Speak to the Statue of Death at the Empyrean Citadel to claim these, with a Constitution and Thieving level of 75, a combat level of 80 and level 75 in the skill you want to receive experience in.

title: Loot Movario's base
description: Completely loot Movario’s base during or upon completion of the While Guthix Sleeps quest. The base is found below McGrubor's Woods.

title: Re-kindle the Dragon Forge in the Ancient cavern
description: A Magic level of 75 is required to re-kindle the forge. For information on how to access the forge, refer to the wiki.

title: Claim Yelps's very own cash bag
description: Yelps can be found on Yu’biusk upon completion of the Mighty Fall. The bag is obtained automatically if Yelps is spared during the quest.

title: Fully enchant your Broomstick
description: Fully enchant the Broomstick received during the Swept Away quest. A Magic level of 93 and completion of the Diamond in the Rough, the Lunar Diplomacy, and the Underground Pass quests is required. Refer to the wiki for further details.

title: Help Guthix open his Chamber of Secrets #2

title: Successfully cook 1500 Cavefish
description: A Fishing level of 85 and a Cooking level of 88 are required.

title: Obtain a full set of Worker robes

title: Obtain a unique from TzHaar

title: Obtain a Scimitops for your Ranch

title: Obtain the Aminishi Miststone
description: Can be bought from the Aminishi Gem Trader costing 1 spice from Player-owned Ports. The spice can be bought from The Arc when you have unlocked Player-owned Ports, costing 350 Chimes and 1 Taijitu.

title: Unlock the ""of the Ithell"" title
description: Craft 100 Crystal flasks.

title: Fully complete the Myths of the White Land
description: Full completion of the quest requires 4 hidden rewards to be obtained. To do this, a Crafting level of 30, an Agility level of 55 and a Woodcutting level of 80 is needed. Speak to Jack the Explorer in the Land of Snow afterwards. Refer to the wiki for reward locations.

title: Super Duper Secret Task #14
description: Help Cecilia decide whether or not to stay at the Abbey upon completion of One Piercing Note.

title: Fully upgrade the Pig creation machine
description: A Construction, Crafting and Summoning level of 84, as well as full completion of Bringing home the Bacon is required to fully upgrade the machine.

title: Thaw 4 frozen hearts
description: Find and Thaw all 4 Frozen Snow Implings in Yeti Town after the completion of Violet is Blue. This requires level 80 in all non-Elite skills.

title: Loot the Trunk in the Azure room of the Temple of Aminishi
description: The trunk key can be found by digging in a mound of sand on the northern part of Aminishi. Access to the Azure room requires partial completion of the Curse of the Black Stone quest.

title: Locate and read the 3 Tarddiad Journals
description: The journals can be found on Tarddiad after the completion of The Light Within. Tarddiad can be accessed through the World Gate, south of the Eagles Peak Lodestone.

title: Fully complete the Fairytale Part III quest
description: Clear two shortcuts, light a fire (requiring 8 Willow logs and a Firemaking level of 85), and loot some herbs and herb seeds (requiring a Herblore level of 85) during or upon completion of the Fairytale Part III quest. The fairy ring codes required for these are CLR, ALP and DIP.

title: Decipher the Murals in the Sunken Temple
description: The four murals can be found on the west Wall of the Sunken Temple after the completion of the Pieces of Hate quest. An Agility, Construction, Firemaking and Thieving level of 85 is required. The Sunken Temple can be accessed via the Rowboat on the south west Beach of Mos Le’Harmless.

title: Uncover the secrets of Haemalchemy
description: Speak to Vanescula Drakan and uncover the secrets of Haemalchemy upon completion of the River of Blood quest.

title: Find and read the “Miscellaneous notes”
description: Collect a total of 15 miscellaneous journals within Daemonheim. A Dungeoneering level of 95 is required. The last 5 letters are not required to complete this achievement.

title: Locate and read the “End of Gara-Dul”
description: The book can be found by searching an Overgrown Idol on Karamja.

title: Obtain the Scabaras Mask and the Was
description: The items are obtained by mining the crack in the room below the Quicksand to access the Scabaras Tomb. A Mining level of 80 and the completion of the Diamond in the Rough quest is required. Refer to the wiki for further details.

title: Claim the three lamps from Azzanadra at the Senntisten Temple
description: Claiming the lamps require the completion of the Temple at Senntisten, the World Wakes, the Fate of the Gods, and the Ritual of the Mahjarrat quests. A skill level of 80 in the chosen Combat skill is required.

title: Translate the murals in the Adamant Dragon dungeon and on Mount Firewake
description: The murals can be translated using a Dragonfire Shield with the Dragonfire Primer. A Firemaking level of 80, and completion of the Ritual of the Mahjarrat, the Fate of the Gods, and the One of a Kind quests is required. A Dragonfire primer can be found in the Library beneath Unferth's house in Burthorpe.

title: Find and inspect all Mahjarrat Deathstones on Freneskae.
description: The stones can be inspected during or upon completion of the Children of Mah quest.

title: Locate the 12 Zaros Memoriam Crystals on Freneskae
description: Freneskae can be accessed through the World Gate.

title: Claim Azzanadra’s Heart
description: Speak to Azzanadra upon completion of the Heart of Stone, the Fate of the Gods, and the Temple of Senntisten quests to claim a lamp. Azzanadra can be found at the Senntisten Temple under the Digsite.

title: Super Duper Secret Task #22
description: Locate an Elite clue scroll using Ava’s Alerter obtained during the Do No Evil quest.

title: Ring up Sliske for enhancements
description: Speak to Sliske with upon completion of the Fate of the Gods quest, the Shadow’s general miniquest, and the Ritual of the Mahjarrat quest to unlock the permanent effect of the Ring of Visibility. Enhance your sixth-age circuit ring by talking to the Guthixian High druid.

title: Obtain the Vyrelord/Vyrelady title
description: Complete all tasks in Darkmeyer to achieve maximum reputation and unlock the Vyrelord/Vyrelady title. Partial completion of the Branches of Darkmeyer quest is required to access Darkmeyer.

title: Locate and read the “Bruce books”
description: Speak to Bruce and inspect Furnace in Edgeville upon completion of the Ritual of the Mahjarrat quest.

title: Locate and interact with the Elder chronicles
description: There are 4 Elder chronicles to interact with spread across Gielinor upon completion of the Fate of the Gods quest. Refer to the wiki for further details.

title: Locate and read the “Acolyte's Diary pages”
description: Inspect all 22 Acolyte's Diary Pages in the Temple of Aminishi (ED1). This can be done in both story- and normal mode. Refer to the wiki for further details.

title: Locate and read all the “Dragonkin Research notes”
description: Inspect all 22 Dragonkin Research Notes in the Dragonkin Laboratory (ED2). This can be done in both story- and normal mode. Refer to the wiki for further details.

title: Locate and read the “Waterlogged Scraps”
description: Inspect all 22 Waterlogged Scraps in the Shadow Reef. This can be done in both story- and normal mode. Refer to the wiki for further details.

title: Hand in 100 Elder chronicles
description: Hand in a total of 100 Elder chronicles to Orla Fairweather, or offer them at  Guthix’s Shrine. Elder chronicles can be obtained while training Divination in the Elder Halls. Freneskae, and the Halls, can be accessed through the World Gate.

title: Locate and read all the “Behemoth notes”
description: Collect all 5 Behemoth notes within Daemonheim. A Dungeoneering level of 101 is required.

title: Unlock the Temple of Light teleport on the Crystal Teleport Seed
description: The teleport can be unlocked by speaking to Eluned or Islywn with a charged seed upon completion of the Within the Light quest.

title: Help Guthix open his Chamber of Secrets #3
description: Learn about Guthix's Core Memories in the Hall of Memories by filling a storage bot. A Divination level of 70 is required to access the Halls. The Corehunting friends chat might be of help.

title: Follow the Gold Brick road
description: Refer to the wiki for details.

title: Unlock all beacon keepers and the entirety of the Beacon network
description: Unlocking the keepers and the entirety of the network is achieved by providing the Keepers with Macaw pouches. Refer to the wiki for a comprehensive list of requirements.

description: An additional 9M GP should be thrown into the Whirlpool. Events are called in the WhirlpoolDnD friends chat. If there is no Whirlpool available, you are allowed to Fish at the Deep sea fishing hub until one is available.

title: Super Duper Secret Task #27
description: Show everyone that Bane is the new black.

title: Harvest 60 fruits from Fruit tree patches within 4 minutes
description: The Master farmer outfit as well as a Giant ent would help massively. You can also use a Supreme growth potions (fruity) to instantly re-grow these fruits. Any type of fruit tree can be used.

title: Activate all Deep Sea Fishing boosts at the same time
description: Deep Sea Fishing boosts can be obtained passively while fishing at the hub, be bought from the Travelling merchant or awarded by participating in the random events occuring at the hub.

title: Complete a lap of the Anachronia agility course in less than seven minutes
description: Going counter-clockwise and using Surge and Bladed dive with the Mobile perk strategically, increases your speed significantly.

title: Complete 25 fully completed Shifting tombs with reward enhancers
description: The reward enhancers can be bought for 1k Dungeoneering tokens each from the Elite Dungeoneering reward shop.

title: Squish a total of 200 Corrupted scarabs
description: Squish a total of 200 Corrupted scarabs. The ‘soulobby’ friends chat can assist with finding these.

title: 'Cry' after harvesting a Lactarius mushroom in the Arc
description: Lactarius mushroom can be obtained from a Mushroom cluster on “The Islands That Once Were Turtles”. A Farming level of 90 is required to harvest it.

title: Defeat the Emberbound soul in the Dragonkin Laboratory while having the Chronicle absorption curse active
description: The emberbound soul is a mini-boss found within the Dragonkin Laboratory. A Prayer level of 87 as well as the completion of the Light Within quest is required.

title: Feed a survivor in the Temple Trekking campsite puzzle some Great maki
description: Only one survivor has to be fed. The Maki requires a Cooking level of 84 to make.

title: Loot 20 urns in a single run of Pyramid Plunder without disturbing a snake.
description: Bringing a Snake charm to charm the urns before searching is highly recommended. The Trahaearn exoskeleton set awarded from Plague's End provides an additional 25% chance to avoid being bitten.

title: Defeat Vanstrom Klause in the Dominion Tower using a reforged Sunspear and wearing the full set of Drakan robes.
description: Fighting Vanstrom in the Dominion Tower, as well as the requested items requires completion of the River of Blood quest.

title: Mock TokHaar-Hok in the Fight Cauldron by defeating him using only Obsidian equipment and luck
description: A Smithing level of 85 completion of the Brink of Extinction quest is required to create the Obsidian equipment.

title: Deliver a Banana pizza to a hungry Highwayman
description: The pizza requires a Cooking level of 85 to make. A highwayman can be found near the farm south of Falador.

title: Taste ALL the baked potatoes
description: Eat all of the available Baked potatoes. Refer to the wiki for a comprehensive list of potatoes to be cooked and tasted. The Mushroom, and Egg potatoes can be obtained from Ascension members, while the rest must be cooked, requiring a Cooking level of 68.

title: Take a bite out of every type of pizza to truly see how superior Pineapple pizza is
description: A Cooking level of 85 is required to create all pizzas. Refer to the wiki for a comprehensive list of pizzas to be made and tasted.

title: Ride a Waka Canoe from Lumbridge to the Wilderness whilst wearing a Straw or Gilded Boater
description: Ride a Waka canoe from Lumbridge to the Wilderness whilst wearing a Straw or Gilded boater. Straw boaters can be found from Medium clues, and Gilded boaters from Master clues.

title: Super Duper Secret Task #32
description: Defeat the King black dragon while wearing Black d'hide in 6 equipmentslots. Good luck!

description: Transform into each of the 8 primates in the Ape Atoll jail using a single Greegree. A Hunter level of 87 is required for this task. Good luck.

description: Light the torches and pray at Guthix’s’ Shrine to pay your respects. A Firemaking level of 74, a Prayer level of 90, and the completion of the World Wakes quest is required.

title: Relieve Sedridor of his remaining stones
description: Obtain all Pure Essence from Archmage Sedridor’s Chest after completing Rune Memories and achieving a Runecrafting level of 99. Archmage Sedridor’s Chest can be found on the 2nd Floor of the Wizards’ Tower.

title: Claim any remaining Dishonourable benefits

title: Help Guthix open his Chamber of Secrets #4
description: Learn about Guthix's Core Memories in the Hall of Memories by filling a storage bot. A Divination level of 70 is required to access the Halls. The Corehunting friends chat might be of help.

title: Open Guthix's Chamber of Secrets #5
description: Learn about Guthix's Core Memories in the Hall of Memories by filling a storage bot. A Divination level of 70 is required to access the Halls. The Corehunting friends chat might be of help.

title: Unlock the Elder campfire boost at War's Retreat
description: A total of 1000 Marks of War and 1000 Elder logs are required to unlock the enhanced effects of the bonfire. If you do not already have the Marks of War, you are allowed to kill the boss you've most recently had a task for, until you have the required marks.

title: Patch the hole in your aquarium with a chinchompa
description: Pull the plug after filling the aquarium will reward you with a Chinchompa plug as well as the Silver barehand fishing emote. Your prawn perks and decorations wont be reset.

title: Find a Cyansoul Kakapo
description: This bird can be found while siphoning Divination springs throughout the Arc.

title: Find a Tortleshell Plover
description: This bird can be found while hunting Tortles in Tortle colonies thoughout the Arc.

title: Find an Azura parrot
description: This bird can be found while cooking Gumbo or Shark soup on fires and ranges throughout the Arc.

title: Find an Awah Guan
description: This bird can be found while mining Sea salt or Alalea salt from Crablets Throughout the Arc.

title: Find a Great Pecker
description: This bird can be found while cutting Bamboo or Golden bamboo throughout the Arc.

title: Catch one of each of the 16 Kami species found throughout the Arc
description: A Hunter level of 95 is required to catch the Orokamis, while a Hunter level of 90 is required for the Bakamis.

title: Help Koschei recover his memories, and test the power of knowledge against Dagannoth Supreme
description: Koschei needs help recovering his memories. This can be done with a Strength and Prayer level of 90 upon completion of the Koschei's troubles miniquest. Defeat Dagannoth Supreme with each of the 4 variants of the Balmung.

title: Traverse gaps, dismantle traps and run laps
description: Complete a lap on the 15 Agility courses listed on the wiki-page of this task. An Agility level of 90 is required.

title: Throw a total of 100M GP into the Whirlpool at the Deep Sea Fishing Hub for good RNG
description: An additional 90M GP should be thrown into the Whirlpool. Events are called in the WhirlpoolDnD friends chat. If there is no Whirlpool available, you are allowed to Fish at the Deep sea fishing hub until one is available.

title: Obtain a streak of 200 in the Fishing Frenzy activity at the Deep Sea Fishing Hub
description: Participating in the activity requires a Fishing level of 94.

title: Mine Light animica rocks and a Diamond in the Trahearn district of Prifddinas
description: The Animica ores becomes available when the Voice of Seren is active in the Trahearn district, during which time the Diamond must also be mined. You are required to mine until the district becomes active.

title: Heat a pair of Unfinished elder rune boots to 100% heat, using the Superheat spell
description: A Smithing level of 90 and one Elder rune bar is required to smith Elder rune boots.

title: Super Duper Secret Task #28
description: Prove to the citizens of Gielinor that the world is a 'safe' place, by looting every single safe in the world. A Thieving level of 96 is required to do this.

title: Get caught and then take your revenge on each of the Big game hunter creatures
description: A Hunter level of 96 and a Slayer level of 76 are required to encounter the Dinosaurs.

title: Complete a Firemaker's log by chopping at least one of each existing log
description: A comprehensive list of the required logs can be found on the wiki. Completing this task requires a Firemaking level of 92 and a Woodcutting level of 90.

title: Enchant a set of all types of gem-tipped bolts
description: A Magic level of 99 and a Fletching level of 99 is required to complete this task. A comprehensive list of the required bolts can be found on the wiki.

title: Runecraft at least one of each known rune
description: A Runecrafting level of 90 and access to Soul runecrafting is required. A comprehensive list of runes needed to be crafted can be found on the wiki.

title: Taste ALL the pies
description: Eat all of the available pies. Refer to the wiki for a comprehensive list of pies to be cooked and tasted. A Cooking level of 90 is required.

title: Taste ALL the meat dishes
description: Eat all of the available Meat dishes. Refer to the wiki for a comprehensive list of dishes to be cooked and tasted. A Cooking level of 91 is required.

title: Super Duper Secret Task #35
description: Fight and defeat the Queen Black Dragon with a Royal crossbow. Good luck!

title: Super Duper Secret Task #37
description: Defeat K'ril Tsuzaroth with a willow weapon. Good luck!

title: Defeat each of the Barrows brothers dealing the killing blow with their own weapon
description: Most weapons should be obtained by this point. If not good luck, and have fun!

title: Bury or scatter at least one of all bones and ashes
description: Ashes and bones obtained inside Daemonheim can be used. Refer to the wiki for a comprehensive list of the required bones and ashes.

description: Training in Char's cave requires the completion of the Firemaker's Curse quest and a Firemaking level of 91.
